benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/invoiceItems/{invoiceItemId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to invoice item

covered: Valid Request: TC01-03 cover successful updates with 204 responses.
Non-Existing Resource and State Variation: TC07, TC24, TC25 cover 404 when item missing or database empty.
Input Validation and Headers: TC06 (invalid invoiceItemId), TC08 (malformed JSON), TC09 (missing header), TC10 (empty body), TC11 (unsupported fields), TC12 (large payload), TC14 (SQL injection).
Idempotency: TC17 covers repeated updates with 204 code.
Edge Case/URL Query Parameters: TC23 (extra URL parameters).
Performance: TC20 (parallel updates) and TC21 (large payload).
Timeout Handling: TC16 covers timeout scenarios.
gaps: Partial Update semantics not explicitly tested (PUT with partial payloads).
Concurrency/Race Conditions: No tests for concurrent edits on the same item.
Rate Limiting: No tests for rate limiting on PUT requests.
Caching Behavior: No tests for ETag/Cache-Control headers.
recommendations: Add a dedicated Partial Update test to verify PUT semantics with partial payloads or restrictions.
Add concurrency tests simulating race conditions on the same invoice item.
Introduce rate-limiting tests to validate throughput and throttling behavior.
Add tests for caching headers on PUT responses (ETag/Cache-Control).
Consider adding explicit 403/Forbidden scenarios to complement 401 Unauthorized coverage.
